  <title>Utilities: Images | Codebase</title>

  <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/holder/2.9.1/holder.min.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.6.3/css/font-awesome.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="theme/css/styles.css">


</head>

<body>

  <!-- @import "site-menubar.kit" -->

  <header class="codebase-docs__header">
    <span><a href="utilities.html">Utilities</a>:</span>
    <h1>Images</h1>
  </header>

  <!-- @import "site-sidebar.kit" -->

  <p>By default, images are set to <code>max-width: 100%</code> of their containing block.</p>

  <img src="holder.js/600x150" alt="">

  <div class="grid grid--gutter grid--nested">
    <div class="col sm--span-6">
      <p>Inline align left:</p>
      <img class="image-align--left" src="holder.js/150x150">
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aenean ut urna ligula. Pellentesque porttitor gravida velit, quis rhoncus quam sollicitudin vitae. Maecenas aliquam vel leo at consequat. Pellentesque placerat diam mi. Praesent finibus semper lectus, id dictum mauris consectetur vel.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col sm--span-6">
      <p>Inline align right:</p>
      <img class="image-align--right" src="holder.js/150x150">
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aenean ut urna ligula. Pellentesque porttitor gravida velit, quis rhoncus quam sollicitudin vitae. Maecenas aliquam vel leo at consequat. Pellentesque placerat diam mi. Praesent finibus semper lectus, id dictum mauris consectetur vel.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Image decoration</h2>

  <p>
    Codebase <code>deco-*</code> <a href="decoration.html">decoration classes</a> can be used on images to achieve interesting effects.
  </p>

  <p>
    A photo frame &ndash; <code>class="deco-b-thick-solid deco-b-white deco-bs"</code>:
  </p>

  <img class="deco-b-thick-solid deco-b-white deco-bs" src="holder.js/600x150">

  <p>
    A centered image &ndash; <code>deco-mh-auto</code>:
  </p>

  <img class="deco-mh-auto" src="holder.js/400x150">

  <div class="grid grid--gutter grid--nested">
    <div class="col sm--span-6">
      <p>Images with rounded corners:</p>

      <div class="grid grid--gutter grid--nested">
        <div class="col sm--span-6">
          <img class="deco-mh-auto deco-b-radius" src="holder.js/150x150">
          <pre><code>deco-b-radius</code></pre>
        </div>
        <div class="col sm--span-6">
          <img class="deco-mh-auto deco-b-thick-solid deco-b-white deco-b-radius deco-bs" src="holder.js/150x150">
          <pre><code>deco-b-thick-solid deco-b-white deco-b-radius deco-bs</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
    <div class="col sm--span-6">
      <p>Images in circles:</p>

      <div class="grid grid--gutter grid--nested">
        <div class="col sm--span-6">
          <img class="deco-mh-auto deco-b-circle" src="holder.js/150x150">
          <pre><code>deco-b-circle</code></pre>
        </div>
        <div class="col sm--span-6">
          <img class="deco-mh-auto deco-b-thick-solid deco-b-white deco-bs deco-b-circle" src="holder.js/150x150">
          <pre><code>deco-b-thick-solid deco-b-white deco-b-circle deco-bs</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- @import "site-footer.kit" -->

</body>

</html>
